OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773947499
OL,3,CDomestic abuse victims to get better
OL,4,Ccourt support in #5m funding boost
OL,6,FDomestic abuse victims will be able to
OL,7,Fget better support as their cases pass
OL,8,Fthrough the courts after the
OL,9,Fgovernment announced #5 million more
OL,10,Fin funding.
OL,12,FMerseyside and Cheshire will be among
OL,13,Fthe first areas in the country to
OL,14,Fpilot the scheme, along with Yorkshire
OL,15,Fand Humber, Wiltshire, Dorset, and the
OL,16,FIsle of Wight.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
