PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773947499
OL,3,CDomestic abuse victims to get better
OL,4,Ccourt support in #5m funding boost
OL,6,FSolicitor General Ellie Reeves said
OL,7,Fthe Crown Prosecution Service would
OL,8,Fget the sum over two years to help
OL,9,Fvictims who have gone to the police
OL,10,Fabout domestic abuse.
OL,12,FThe Government wants to target the
OL,13,Ffunding at "the most serious" domestic
OL,14,Fabuse, it is understood.
OL,16,FThe scheme will mean victims of crime
OL,17,Fwill be able to meet prosecutors ahead
OL,18,Fof crown court trials. It is hoped
OL,19,Fthis means victims will be able to ask
OL,20,Fquestions about the court process.
OL,26,@uD@LOUuD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773947499
OL,3,CDomestic abuse victims to get better
OL,4,Ccourt support in #5m funding boost
OL,6,FThere will also be more domestic abuse
OL,7,Fvictim liaison officers.
OL,9,FSpeaking in the House of Commons, Ms
OL,10,FReeves said the changes would mean
OL,11,Fvictims' "voices are heard" and would
OL,12,Fhelp prevent them dropping out of
OL,13,Fcourt cases.
OL,15,FShe continued: "This offer is already
OL,16,Favailable to victims of rape and
OL,17,Fserious sexual assault across the
OL,18,Fcountry.
OL,26,@sD@JOUsD@[O]wD@POU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773947499
OL,3,CDomestic abuse victims to get better
OL,4,Ccourt support in #5m funding boost
OL,6,F"I know from speaking with prosecutors
OL,7,Fand victims the difference these
OL,8,Fmeetings can make, and I'm pleased to
OL,9,Fsee it extended to victims of domestic
OL,10,Fabuse."
OL,12,FLabour MP for Congleton Sarah Russell,
OL,13,Fwho asked about increasing prosecution
OL,14,Frates for violence against women and
OL,15,Fgirls, said: "I very much welcome that
OL,16,Fnews. The prosecution rates for cases
OL,17,Finvolving violence against women and
OL,18,Fgirls are shamefully low.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@GO]wD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773947499
OL,3,CDomestic abuse victims to get better
OL,4,Ccourt support in #5m funding boost
OL,6,F"I strongly welcome the Government's
OL,7,Fambition to tackle violence against
OL,8,Fwomen and girls."
OL,10,FKate Brown, the Crown Prosecution
OL,11,FService's national lead for domestic
OL,12,Fabuse, said: "For many victims of
OL,13,Fdomestic abuse, the path to justice
OL,14,Fmight feel overwhelming. After such
OL,15,Fisolating and frightening experiences,
OL,16,Fthe criminal justice system must be a
OL,17,Fplace where victims feel supported,
OL,18,Fheard and able to move forward.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@QO]tD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
