PN,39406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773947499
OL,3,CDomestic abuse victims to get better
OL,4,Ccourt support in #5m funding boost
OL,6,F"Today's funding announcement shows
OL,7,Fthe real difference support for
OL,8,Fvictims makes. By expanding existing
OL,9,Fpilots, we are making sure more
OL,10,Fdomestic abuse victims feel informed
OL,11,Fand protected at every stage."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@^O]
